nodes.text: Iesei was a Killik hive that lived on the planet Tatooine during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. During the Swarm War, the Iesei lived on a desert planet that came under Chiss attack.

In Star Wars: The Old Republic both Vector Hyllus and Daizanna pronounce the name of the nest as "Lesei", mistaking the uppercase "I" for lowercase "L". This is an obvious mistake, as all known Killik names are proper palindromes.
